wikipedia_page.main: Sarah Walker (born 29 March 1974) is a property investor, broadcaster and freelance property writer, best known for her role in To Buy or Not to Buy.

response: The original presenter teams was Dominic Littlewood with Kristian Digby, who were joined by Sarah Walker at the end of the first series, as 10 hour-long 'specials' were made, with Walker doing makeover on the contributing couples' house as they househunted with Digby and Littlewood.
